Comment: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.03,Default,sc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}鼓動的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.03,Default,tc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}鼓動的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.52,0:24:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}期盼之人
